data.name: RichTextBox_About.Text
data.value:
The tool simulates the Xbox controller through ViGEmBus, allowing users to play the piano in CODEVEIN, written by HaoJun0823 through C# (.NET 4.5.2). Hope CODEVEIN can develop into a great game in the future! I hope there is more new content!
Author's note: Love my son Okami Yuuki forever!
Piano Technical By Inanko Tested on game version 1.53.93354 Windows10 1909 X64 (Steam version) AMD CPU and NVIDIA GPU. Please right-click the file to view the version number.
Homepage: https://blog.haojun0823.xyz Github: https://github.com/HaoJun0823/CODEVEIN-Piano-Helper
